      "content": "i don't think a break is gonna help. it's not like i'm tired, it's just... i feel like i'm just occupying space. like, i'm part of the background noise of the city. if the noise just stopped, the city would keep moving exactly the same. it's like i'm already gone, just not physically yet. does that even make sense?",
